WEBVTT

00:00:29.200 --> 00:00:31.105
Today to share his recipe for happiness,

00:00:31.129 --> 00:00:34.519
joining us from New York 
is the world famous Indian chef,

00:00:34.520 --> 00:00:36.160
Vikas Khanna.

00:00:36.249 --> 00:00:37.559
Vikas Khanna.

00:00:37.630 --> 00:00:46.140
(Applause)

00:00:47.880 --> 00:00:51.359
Vikas Khanna: 
I was born in Amritsar in 1971.

00:00:52.080 --> 00:00:54.639
Right in the middle
of the Indo-Pakistani war.

00:00:55.560 --> 00:00:57.465
When I was born, the doctor saw me

00:00:57.489 --> 00:01:01.449
and told my mom
that the baby's feet are deformed.